&lt;p&gt;Attention, &lt;strong&gt;CNAs (PRN available)&lt;/strong&gt;: make the move to a Great Place to Work, bringing your skills to our senior living community’s health center. There, you’ll serve as part of an amazing nursing team providing patient-centered care and services to residents in our assisted living, memory support, and/or skilled nursing neighborhoods. We offer a supportive workplace culture, as well as a competitive hourly rate, benefits, and on-the-job perks.&lt;/p&gt;
